{"tid":1836751,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"網購日本口罩介紹","createTime":"2020-01-23T10:17:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-22T10:08:58.000Z","uid":255764,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"3b8c717188c8d066011478be85dc19000ef3d0ec","tid":1836751,"uid":255764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:17:18.000Z","msg":"利申：<br />\n本人唔係專業人士 只係睇咗啲資料參考<br />\n唔忍心大家出街買俾人呃買大陸野<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n特別鳴謝 @gfhk_hkdesign<br />\n佢地個post好有參考嘅作用<br />\n請大家like佢地ig大大力支持<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/p/B7nXZUGgXrd/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB7nXZUGgXrd%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=1ea68bff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fp%2FB7nXZUGgXrd%2F&h=a6ce80ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/p/B7nXZUGgXrd/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qrpEOa4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqrpEOa4.png&h=2390872e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XKFXzRf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXKFXzRf.png&h=d05dbc89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日中午係amazon jp<br />\n仲係賣緊around 2000yen 50個<br />\n明顯以家開始加價同無貨<br />\nM size 175mm （正常口罩size）<br />\nM-S size 160mm<br />\nS size 145mm （細面女仔啱用）<br />\n另外都有啲小朋友嘅size但未見有大盒個種<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/stores/node/2331582051?_encoding=UTF8&amp;field-lbr_brands_browse-bin=三次元マスク&amp;ref_=bl_dp_s_mw_2331582051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fstores%2Fnode%2F2331582051%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26field-lbr_brands_browse-bin%3D%E4%B8%89%E6%AC%A1%E5%85%83%E3%83%9E%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%26ref_%3Dbl_dp_s_mw_2331582051&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=6835e74e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/stores/node/2331582051?_encoding=UTF8&amp;field-lbr_brands_browse-bin=三次元マスク&amp;ref_=bl_dp_s_mw_2331582051</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L0j9qYY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL0j9qYY.png&h=584737a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個我自己無買 大家如果有買可以補充多啲資料<br />\n都係有分3個size<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/stores/node/2328152051?_encoding=UTF8&amp;field-lbr_brands_browse-bin=超立体マスク&amp;ref_=bl_dp_s_mw_2328152051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fstores%2Fnode%2F2328152051%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26field-lbr_brands_browse-bin%3D%E8%B6%85%E7%AB%8B%E4%BD%93%E3%83%9E%E3%82%B9%E3%82%AF%26ref_%3Dbl_dp_s_mw_2328152051&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=54cd40cf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/stores/node/2328152051?_encoding=UTF8&amp;field-lbr_brands_browse-bin=超立体マスク&amp;ref_=bl_dp_s_mw_2328152051</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7JP11zp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7JP11zp.png&h=fa995a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eSgPq05.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeSgPq05.png&h=4afe2df3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外就係無名博士介紹呢款<br />\n博士研究好多文具野非常專業<br />\n歡迎大家大大力like page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/692288617886543/posts/837336223381781/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F692288617886543%2Fposts%2F837336223381781%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=4cd66ccf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/692288617886543/posts/837336223381781/</a><br />\n<br />\nLink: <br />\n<a href=\"https://item.rakuten.co.jp/suzuken/10000116/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitem.rakuten.co.jp%2Fsuzuken%2F10000116%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=4dfc1dc2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://item.rakuten.co.jp/suzuken/10000116/</a><br />\n（原link齊款 但只有日本樂天有）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B00AJB06DQ/ref=mp_s_a_1_1?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=1579774480&amp;sr=8-1&amp;srs=2684312051\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fdp%2FB00AJB06DQ%2Fref%3Dmp_s_a_1_1%3F_encoding%3DUTF8%26qid%3D1579774480%26sr%3D8-1%26srs%3D2684312051&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=13d18382\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/dp/B00AJB06DQ/ref=mp_s_a_1_1?_encoding=UTF8&amp;qid=1579774480&amp;sr=8-1&amp;srs=2684312051</a><br />\n（日馬得女人size）<br />\n<br />\n集運我係用buyandship嘅<br />\n又快又平 只要到咗倉3幾日就會到香港先<br />\n喺香港再集運 感覺好似快好多<br />\n<br />\n分享完畢 有錯勿屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歡迎大家再分享多啲日本口罩<br />\n<br />\n有咗集運其實係樂天買都得<br />\n<a href=\"https://global.rakuten.com/zh-tw/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fglobal.rakuten.com%2Fzh-tw%2F&d=BfE6afXCHr80cM3PNjd%2Fp7c9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=de8b9949\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://global.rakuten.com/zh-tw/</a><br />\n唔洗一定要揀番直寄香港"},{"pid":"6d126e45273e0340903f68d1bcebb34212cff887","tid":1836751,"uid":255764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:20:06.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"27fa44510b5ef42b98bf952802d521dc145f6ba6","tid":1836751,"uid":113784,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:22:50.000Z","msg":"唔識用日文amazon <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd2a2b49b2e2174aa9e9a1dea296d8c5937e1938","tid":1836751,"uid":124768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T10:27:45.000Z","msg":"三次元係咪獨立包裝"},{"pid":"3aeb40fb858daa7320fca294fa900f015e9db526","tid":1836751,"uid":50598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dd2a2b49b2e2174aa9e9a1dea296d8c5937e1938","tid":1836751,"uid":124768,"lik